<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- لَا إِنْ مَلَكُوهُ مِنْ مُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَلَا يُعَادُ عَالِيًا لَوْ انْهَدَمَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ بَنَى مُسْلِمٌ دَارًا عِنْدَهُمْ دُونَ بِنَائِهِمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَمِنْ إِحْدَاثِ كَنَائِسَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَبِنَاءِ مَا انْهَدَمَ مِنْهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَمِنْ إِظْهَارِ مُنْكَرٍ، وَعِيدٍ، وَصَلِيبٍ، وَأَكْلٍ وَشُرْبٍ نَهَارَ رَمَضَانَ، وَخَمْرٍ، وَخَنْزِيرٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَرَفْعِ صَوْتٍ عَلَى مَيْتٍ، وَقِرَاءَةِ قُرْآنٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٨]</span> وَنَاقُوسٍ، وَجَهْرٍ بِكِتَابِهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٩]</span> وَشِرَاءِ مُصْحَفٍ، وَفِقْهٍ، وَحَدِيثٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَعَلَى الإِمَامِ حِفْظُهُمْ، وَمَنْعُ مَنْ يُؤْذِيهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> مَنْ أَبَى مُنْهُمْ بَذْلَ الِجزْيَةِ، أَوْ الصَّغَارَ، أَوِ الْتِزَامَ حُكْمِنَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> أَوْ قَاتَلَنَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> أَوْ زَنَى بِمُسْلِمَةٍ، أَوْ أَصَابَهَا بِاسْمِ نِكَاحٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>